title: SmackDAHN Happened, Ian Rapaport, and Dalvin Cook. Happy Monday
description: Fresh off of my Friday Night SmackDAHN debut, I chit chat about my thoughts on it all. Twitter breaking, reactions, expectations going forward and all of that happy stuff.. Nigel Seeley, known soccer bettor and  British fella, stops by to explain what the hell the European Super League is. Ian Rapaport brings all the tea in the NFL world. Dalvin Cook stops by for an absolutely fantastic conversation about the current state of the NFL and also his offseason.. AJ Hawk joins us to discuss all things happening in his world/the world. Not a bad show for a Monday. I appreciate you allowing us in your earholes. Cheers.
